headline: Fire reported at Phillips 66's Los Angeles refinery

headline: Voyager acquires stake in 254-mile Panola Pipeline and secures credit facility
summary: The 254-mile (408.7km) Panola Pipeline transports Y-Grade NGLs from Panola County to Mont Belvieu in Texas.

headline: Phillips 66 Confirms Los Angeles Refinery Shutdown by October
summary: PSX to shut its LA refinery by October, raising concerns about fuel supply and price spikes in California amid strong seasonal demand and refinery maintenance.
